{"word":"G4453 - πωλέω - pōléō - po-leh'-o - Sell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πωλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pōléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">po-leh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வில்"},{"paragraph":"to barter, to sell"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably ultimately from <b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>pelomai</b> (to <i>be busy</i>, to <i>trade</i>); to <i>barter</i> (as a <i>pedlar</i>), that is, to <i>sell:</i> - sell, whatever is sold.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}